description.narrative:
&nbsp;
This project strengthens the social organizations, indigenous and Afro-Colombian of the Department of Choc&oacute;, and especially in the area of influence of Cocomacia, so that they participate and influence the negotiating processes of the Government with the guerrillas of the ELN and the implementation of agreements with the FARC guerrillas in their territories. It motivates the involvement of organizations in the implementation of the ethnic chapter of peace, recognition of collective rights of victims, the articulation of plans of departmental and municipal development plans of ethno-development organizations, as a contribution to a stable and lasting peace in the Choc&oacute; department. Looking for ethnic authorities constribuyan to "good living" in a climate of peace, with a high level of participation in the construction of the PDETS and defense and conservation of natural resources affected by the armed conflict and the extractivism. Cocomacia and FISCH built in previous years the Regional Agenda of Peace, as a proposal from organizations for the construction of peace in its territory; now they seek that this proposal should be included in the policies of the post agreements.
&nbsp;
